h3cVsi.name: h3cVsi
h3cVsi.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
h3cVsi.description: The MIB for VSI (Virtual Switch Instance).

h3cVsiNextAvailableVsiIndex.name: h3cVsiNextAvailableVsiIndex
h3cVsiNextAvailableVsiIndex.description: Next available VSI entry index for creating VSI. Its value ranges from 0x1 to 0xFFFFFFFF.The invalid value 0xFFFFFFFF indicates that no VSI entry can be created.

h3cVsiTable.name: h3cVsiTable
h3cVsiTable.description: A table for configuring VSI parameters.

h3cVsiEntry.name: h3cVsiEntry
h3cVsiEntry.description: An entry for configuring VSI parameters.

h3cVsiIndex.name: h3cVsiIndex
h3cVsiIndex.description: Index of VSI. Its value ranges from 0x1 to 0xFFFFFFFE.

h3cVsiName.name: h3cVsiName
h3cVsiName.description: Name of VSI. Max string length of VSI name is 31.

h3cVsiMode.name: h3cVsiMode
h3cVsiMode.description: Mode of VSI. Martini mode indicated this VSI support VPLS service signalled using LDP, kompella indicated this VSI support VPLS service signalled using BGP, minm indicated this VSI support MAC-in-MAC service.

h3cMinmIsid.name: h3cMinmIsid
h3cMinmIsid.description: The MAC-in-MAC I-SID of VSI in minm or martiniAndMinm mode. It must be different for every VSI. Its value ranges from 0x1 to 0xFFFFFF. In other VSI mode, its value is invalid value 0x0.

h3cVsiId.name: h3cVsiId
h3cVsiId.description: Identifier of VSI in martini or martiniAndMinm mode, by default, it's the PW ID of this VSI. Its value ranges from 1 to 4294967295. In other VSI mode, its value is invalid value 0.

h3cVsiEnableHubSpoke.name: h3cVsiEnableHubSpoke
h3cVsiEnableHubSpoke.description: Config HubSpoke property of this VSI.

h3cVsiAdminState.name: h3cVsiAdminState
h3cVsiAdminState.description: Set VSI admin state as adminUp or adminDown.

h3cVsiRowStatus.name: h3cVsiRowStatus
h3cVsiRowStatus.description: Operation status of this table entry.

h3cVsiXconnectTable.name: h3cVsiXconnectTable
h3cVsiXconnectTable.description: A table for configuring xconnect parameters.

h3cVsiXconnectEntry.name: h3cVsiXconnectEntry
h3cVsiXconnectEntry.description: An entry for configuring xconnect parameters. Each entry means connecting a service instance of a interface to a VSI.

h3cVsiXconnectIfIndex.name: h3cVsiXconnectIfIndex
h3cVsiXconnectIfIndex.description: Index of the interface associated with the VSI.

h3cVsiXconnectEvcSrvInstId.name: h3cVsiXconnectEvcSrvInstId
h3cVsiXconnectEvcSrvInstId.description: Index of the service instance associated with the VSI.

h3cVsiXconnectVsiName.name: h3cVsiXconnectVsiName
h3cVsiXconnectVsiName.description: Name of VSI. Max string length of VSI name is 31.

h3cVsiXconnectAccessMode.name: h3cVsiXconnectAccessMode
h3cVsiXconnectAccessMode.description: Access mode of this service instance.

h3cVsiXconnectHubSpoke.name: h3cVsiXconnectHubSpoke
h3cVsiXconnectHubSpoke.description: Config HubSpoke property of this service instance.

h3cVsiXconnectRowStatus.name: h3cVsiXconnectRowStatus
h3cVsiXconnectRowStatus.description: Operation status of this table entry.
